Precise and relatively simple temperature calibration is a key advantage of the PCTC method compared to other techniques that require extensive temperature calibration. To calibrate the crystallization temperature \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
